Save The Planes
    In this game you must protect the planes at all cost. Make sure to dodge the explosions falling from the sky but
    try to get more health by catching the hearts. As you play longer they start falling faster.

List of files:
    final_game
    buttons
    health
    obstacle_1
    score
    settings
    ship_1
    ship_1

    In order to start make sure you press the bright red start button on the first page.

